Scenario: You are an executive of the company and employees are excessively using social media during work hours on their work computers. This is having a negative impact on productivity. The new policy is that employees are not allowed to access social media accounts while at work. Explain the problems associated with accessing social media during work hours (you have the liberty to use figures...be somewhat realistic).\
