To: All Employees\
From: Tyler Lewis, Executive People-Manager\
Date: March 4, 2024\
Subject: [UPDATE] Company-Wide Implementation of Social Media Usage Policy\
\
Dear Team,\
\
As part of our ongoing efforts to maximize productivity and efficiency within our company, it has become necessary to address the issue of excessive social media usage during work hours. A new policy regarding social media access while at work will be implemented.\
\
