\f1\b \cf0 Effective immediately, employees are prohibited from accessing personal social media accounts, including but not limited to Facebook, Twitter (X), Instagram, LinkedIn, during designated work hours.
\f0\b0  \
This policy applies to all company-owned devices and networks.\
