In recent months, it has come to our attention that a significant portion of our workforce is spending excessive time on social media platforms during work hours. While occasional breaks are understandable and even encouraged for mental refreshment, the extent to which social media has been accessed during working hours is having a detrimental impact on overall productivity.\
\
\
\ul Problems Associated with Accessing Social Media During Work Hours:\ulnone \
\
